    32→## Intro<a name="intro"></a>
    34→Tomli is a Python library for parsing [TOML](https://toml.io).
    35→Version 2.4.0 and later are compatible with [TOML v1.1.0](https://toml.io/en/v1.1.0).
    36→Older versions are [TOML v1.0.0](https://toml.io/en/v1.0.0) compatible.
    37→
